Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:17.80,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,This castle looks a lot smaller from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:22.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,Morning, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:25.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sorry Spike,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:27.86,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm still trying to find my way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:30.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You don't happen to know where the library is, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:32.99,Spike,,0,0,0,,Next door on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:35.70,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:37.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Acceptance,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:39.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,altruism — definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:42.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starlight, good morning, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:43.23,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.85,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I got a little turned around.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:47.77,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe you're letting me stay here…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:49.20,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,as your pupil…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:51.70,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,after everything I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:55.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not one to dwell on the past. And neither should you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:57.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The castle is your home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:59.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And as far as being my pupil goes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:02.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to figure out what your first friendship lesson should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:05.68,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, it looks like you're narrowing it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:07.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, this are just the "A"s.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:09.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,After this I move on to the "B"s.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:55.64,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know I'm just learning about friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:59.05,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,but I didn't think there are this many lessons for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:00.54,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,How do we choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:03.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should pare things down a bit before we go through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:06.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join the others in the throne room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.03,0:02:10.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They're planning our trip to the Crystal Empire when Shining Armor and Princess Cadence have their baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.99,0:02:12.35,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Throne room! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:17.35,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Which way is the throne room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well I think we should leave ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna miss the Chrystaling!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:26.92,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But, um, shouldn't we wait for the invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:31.44,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Frankly I'm not exacly clear on all the customs and traditions of the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:33.72,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Especially when it comes to the Chrystaling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:35.21,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What's a Chrystaling?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:37.56,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just it, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:40.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadence's and Shining Armor's baby is due any day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:42.67,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and we're still not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:46.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Empire was gone for a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,A lot of their customs are a bit murky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We know it's got something to do with the new baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:52.72,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.22,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.22,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.48,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And some kind of cool energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:03:00.32,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,A-a-and a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's not hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.35,Spike,,0,0,0,,Most things in a Crystal Empire aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:11.18,Spike,,0,0,0,,Like how I'm a big hero there, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.58,0:03:20.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,Plus I'd had to help Twilight do a lot of research about Chrystalings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:24.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,Whenever a baby is born in the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,the parents bring it before the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:29.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,They get the purest shard of crystal they can find,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:33.61,Spike,,0,0,0,,then pick a Crystaller to present the baby to everypony who comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:36.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,Then they all share the light and joy they feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:41.10,Spike,,0,0,0,,feeding it to the crystal, that joins with the Heart and increases it's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.79,Spike,,0,0,0,,And this is going to be a royal Chrystaling,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:46.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,so pretty much the whole Empire will show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,That hasn't have been in a millenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:52.46,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What do you mean it increases Crystal Heart's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:55.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,The energy it uses to protect the Crystal Empire, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.19,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Protected from what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:04:00.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,I didn't helped Twilight with that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.65,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Hey Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:11.17,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,can I ask you something about the Crystal Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:13.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Funny you should mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:16.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Because I've just narrowed your first friendship lesson down to three options.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:18.86,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And one of them is in the Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.65,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I found out that's where the first pony you ever cared about lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.17,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sunburst?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course that's just one idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We could also go to Griffonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:31.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Making friends with a griffon is a challenge all by itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:36.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Or we could tag along with the CMC's the next time they try to help a pony figure out why they're special…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:42.09,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, no…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.80,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Those all sound great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:44.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I guess you were right. It is gonna be hard to chose one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:51.03,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:07.37,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I am never gonna find my way around this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,Gee, Starlight, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:10.91,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:14.53,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Twilight's figuring out what's my first friendship lesson is, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:17.57,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm not exactly thrilled with the options.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:20.08,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Well, with one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:21.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.57,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Reuniting me with my first friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's so terrible about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:32.52,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,When we were foals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:36.35,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sunburst knew everyhting there was to know about magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.86,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,He always knew just what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:58.91,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,And he was always there to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:12.93,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not surprising that Sunburst got his cutie mark in magic and…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.76,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,went off to Princes Celestia's school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:17.79,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But when he left…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:20.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,You blamed cutiemarks and stripped the whole village of their,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:24.53,Spike,,0,0,0,,so when Twilight and the others stopped you, you went back in time and almost destroyed Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.18,0:06:28.65,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Not realy stuff I'm super eager to tell Sunburst about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:32.95,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I mean, he's probably some big important wizard now and…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:36.34,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I can't even find my way around Twilight's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, if Sunburst is that good at magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,maybe he'd appreciate your…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,exploits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:45.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,You should talk to Twilight about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'd want to hear what you have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.13,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:51.88,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But I don't want her to think I'm not ready to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:54.71,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Or that I'm not grateful for everything she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike! Come quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:09.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's a Crystalling invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Shining armor is a father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm an aunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:14.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, this settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:16.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Since we're going to the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,you first friendship lesson is going to be…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,reuniting with Sunburst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:24.01,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Great…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.50,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Um, Applejack,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.68,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, just a little somethin' for the young'un.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:51.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Made from genuine Sweet Apple Acres apple trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,We make 'em for all the Apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.15,0:07:56.47,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And any pony related to Twilight is practically family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:59.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:02.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But it's no Cloudsdale mobile!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:06.16,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.85,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, a mobile is real nice…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:14.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,as long as you have somethin' to lay in so you can look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:17.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And a fetching blanket to keep you warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Shining Armor and Princess Cadance will love all our gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I think they're more happy that we'll be attending the baby's Crystalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:30.49,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Ooh! I can't wait to see all that light and love make the Crystal Heart even more sparkly and shiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:34.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Actually, Pinkie, the Crystal Heart is an ancient and powerful relic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:38.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Without its magic, the Crystal Empire would be lost to the Frozen North.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:42.70,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Wow, this Crystalling sounds pretty important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:45.94,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'd understand if you wanted to… you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.94,0:08:49.71,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,wait to do a different friendship lesson when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? This trip is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:58.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not only do I get to see the baby and take part in the ceremony that helps maintain the magic of the Crystal Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:02.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but I'm starting my new pupil off with the most amazing friendship lesson ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:03.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.50,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.66,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Me neither…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:12.88,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Actually, Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:16.30,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I am a little worried about meeting Sunburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:19.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, trust me, I know what it's like to see old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I'll be right there to help things along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:24.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've broken the whole lesson down into a few easy steps
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:27.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,to ensure this reunion is going without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:39.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Step one: head to Sunburst's house and get you two started on the right hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:42.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Step two: get to the castle with enough time to visit the ba…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.48,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Twilight!..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were meeting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.24,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:51.76,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,It's me… right here…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:54.76,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Here I am! Why wouldn't I am come meet my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:57.00,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Though we have meet before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:58.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you allright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:09:59.52,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Never better!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:03.15,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Being a father is amazing and wonderful… and amazing…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.15,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,and confusing…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:07.56,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,And amazing! But surprising too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:08.99,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I mean, not that you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:11.07,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,You would known, I know… You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.25,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:17.05,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I haven't really slept since Cadence had the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:20.11,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Come of think of it, she hasn't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:22.17,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,It sure would be great to get a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:25.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of Course. I don't know what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:28.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You two probably need all kinds of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, Starlight, but I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:33.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,combining your first lesson with this visit wasn't such a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.29,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:38.01,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,You're an aunt now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:42.04,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That's way more important than some friendship lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:44.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just wish there was a way to do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:48.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:51.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,You've already done the work for Starlight's lesson with this list.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.12,Spike,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:56.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike you are genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.21,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.42,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Genius…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:03.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Than it's settled. Shining Armor and I will head straight to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And you two can head straight to Sunburst's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:06.99,Spike,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:15.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Alright, big brother. Let's go see this amazing baby pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.30,Spike,,0,0,0,,I know you're a little worried about this reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure Twilight's got everything covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:30.84,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Everything except how I'd rather do absolutely anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.72,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, I bet she's taken that into account too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.50,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's all part of the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.10,Spike,,0,0,0,,Trust the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.34,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:46.17,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Hey i-is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh… yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:48.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Now, according to the list Sunburst's house is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:54.43,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Why is there a statue of you in the Crystal Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:59.79,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Because Spike the Brave and Glorious saved all of us from King Sombra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:02.44,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And than again during the Equestria Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:03.39,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.40,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Really. Big fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:09.02,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Um, when were you gonna tell me about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It most certainly is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:15.98,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:20.05,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We are not going anywhere until I get the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:26.06,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Before we go in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:28.78,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I should probably tell you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:32.10,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Seeing the baby might be a bit of a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:35.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, big brother, I've met babies before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:38.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I expect meeting this one won't be any different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:47.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course, I could be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:57.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The baby is an alicorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.90,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,It looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:03.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But… But… But I thought alicorn wings had to be earned
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:06.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,by accomplishing some great princess-worthy deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:09.31,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yeah. How can you just be born with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:13.24,Celestia,,0,0,0,,The birth of an alicorn is something Equestria has never seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:15.82,Luna,,0,0,0,,It is beyond even our understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.21,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,That's not very reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:20.78,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wow! A unicorn! And a pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:22.76,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,So she can be a superstrong flyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:24.83,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And have crazy baby magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:28.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Well, I know all about superstrong flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I can help keep tabs on her magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:47.75,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It appears her magic is more powerful than that of a newborn unicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:49.91,Luna,,0,0,0,,The crowds have already started together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:55.14,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This Crystalling is gonna be some party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.13,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Do you think we should call it off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:03.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Uhm, we've all faced a lot worse than baby magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:07.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine cancelling such a beautiful and important ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:10.06,Rarity,,0,0,0,,over something so potentially adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:14.75,Celestia,,0,0,0,,In light of the little one's abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.97,Celestia,,0,0,0,,this Cristalling might be more important than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:21.36,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you should address your subjects and remind them of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:33.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Shinig Armor, do you have everything you need for the ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:35.98,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.07,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I still have to interview the honor guards,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:41.43,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,choose the purity crystal, and pick a crystaller!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,All right, take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie can stay here with me and keep an eye on the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:52.14,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And we'll all help you with everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.52,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Baby…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:59.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,That is, if you can stay awake long enough to tell us how.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:02.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,And that's how we found the Crystal Heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:04.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,defeated King Sombra and saved the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:07.27,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We love you, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:10.90,SomeponyYellow,,0,0,0,,Tell the one about the Equestria Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:14.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, as much as I love reliving my heroic deeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,Starlight and I have an important lesson to do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:19.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,by order of a Princess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:24.64,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, Spike. I wanna hear about the Games too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,I know you're nervous about seeing Sunburst,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.08,Spike,,0,0,0,,but it says right in step three to…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:32.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,Deal with your fears by facing them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,not by putting it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.48,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Let's go get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:45.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:48.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,Knocking on the door isn't the next thing on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.08,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:52.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,I know Twilight can be a little nitpicky,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:54.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,but this is your first lesson as her pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:56.65,Spike,,0,0,0,,And it's important that we do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.32,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.21,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What's the next thing on the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,Before they see each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,make sure to highlight the importance of the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:08.73,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure we can skip that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.46,Spike,,0,0,0,,I mean, if we skip it the whole lesson could go south.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:15.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,And then you might wind up taking a giant step backwards instead of forwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:18.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll never be able to learn anything about friendship at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:23.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's almost like your whole future depends on this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,Highlight the importance of the meeting. Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that you wanted to skip that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:43.70,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Sunburst?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:46.23,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Yes. What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:49.60,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It's… It's me. Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:52.39,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,We used to be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:56.64,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course. S-Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.67,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,My goodness. It…It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.37,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,What… What… What you've been up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:05.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Me? Oh. You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:08.03,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Some of this. Some of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:10.55,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Different stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:14.04,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Right now I'm sort of Twilight Sparkle's new pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:16.29,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,The Princess of Friendship?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:20.81,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's actually kind of why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:23.99,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I mean I know you're probably very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:25.24,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.61,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Well. I figured after Magic School
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:30.37,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,you've gone on to do important wizard work, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:32.23,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Oh. No. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.90,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's me. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:39.60,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Important wizard. Really busy with lot of… wizarding… stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:43.25,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Right. Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.63,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Good to see, you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:51.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should have skipped the highlighting of importance of the meeting after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.55,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Well. I guess that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,Starlight. Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:58.42,Spike,,0,0,0,,We have to at least to explain what Twilight wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.15,0:18:08.80,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Dearest citizens,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:13.22,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I am sure you are all just as thrilled and ready for this Crystalling
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.76,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,as myself and Shining Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:23.99,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I'm not ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.27,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.62,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Just pick whoever looks the most, like, honor guard material.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.35,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Right. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.52,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:38.91,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Fatherhood is way more stressful than I ever thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.89,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I can only imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:45.64,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now, I know choosing the crystal of purity is a very important decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:50.25,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So I've gone throught the trouble of arranging them in order from incredibly pure
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:52.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,to outrageously pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:56.19,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Um, Rarity, don't they all sort of look the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:59.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh well, to the untrained eye, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:01.35,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Shining Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.53,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I don't know!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:09.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I hope Twilight and Pinkie are having better luck with the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:14.72,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Well… at least she's having… fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pinkie, hold her still!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:27.27,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I'm trying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:36.72,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Sooooo…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:41.55,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,The princess of friendship wants you an I to be friends again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:44.15,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.15,0:19:45.50,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Weird, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:47.51,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:50.85,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Did something happen to you after I left for magic school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.85,0:19:52.05,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:55.01,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't see what that has to do with anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:56.51,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Why would you even ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:03.85,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I mean, did something happen to you after you left for magic school?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:06.24,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,What? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:10.66,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Like you said, I'm an… important… wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:15.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there's something on Twilight's list that can help here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:25.43,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.74,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,I chose the honor guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:27.89,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,picked the purity crystal,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.88,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,And I know exactly who I want to be our crystaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:33.02,ShiningArmor,,0,0,0,,So, all we need is…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.35,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,The baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:37.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.51,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,She's a reeeally strong flyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:15.91,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing that's gonna make it hard to do the crystalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's worse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:22.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Without the Heart, the Crystal Empire is about to be buried under a mountain of ice and snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:38.50,Auto,,0,0,0,,СЧАСТЛИВЫЙ ПОНЕЦ
